PhP720 (covers six classes) if paid to any authorized FFA officers* on
or before May 17, Monday. People who avail of the early bird discount
also qualify for the commemorative <span style="font-style: italic;">tanto</span> that will be awarded to 20 students who manage to attend 100% of seminar sessions. </span><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;">*Authorized
